assessment_details.task_description:
The purpose of this assessment is to develop your critical reflective skills. Being a highly reflective practitioner who can articulate workplace learnings, will help you grow professionally and extend your workplace skills and knowledge.

Your reflections will need to:

contain detailed descriptions of incidents/issues/challenges/successes you encountered during your workplace experience, and how you reacted to them;

discuss your frustrations and consequent growth with regards to the incidents/issues/challenges/successes you chose to document;

ask probing questions about yourself and your future work options;

reflect on how your workplace experience may impact your future career choices.

​You will use a reflective method such as SEAL.
